      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DR. WARREN (1) is a talented type and proved too classy last time to win by 5.5 lengths at this track in a handy 28.91 beating MARYVALE GIRL. Recorded the quickest time on the card last start. Great chance to get the job done again. BALLISTIC BRAX (6) crossed over from out wide last start before finishing third (29.59) at this track in a Mix 6/7 over 510m. The form out of his last race has been franked. Expected to be in this for a long way. ELIJAH ROSE (2) is mixing form, finishing out of the placings latest but was a winner three back and returns to Sale this time where he has performed well. Has the ability and looks a key chance here. MINTER'S JET (4) can fill a top-three spot.",
